  story {
    writer {
      name: "Hayao Miyazaki"
    }
    rating: "Good"
    comments: "The concept is good as the movie is a allegory for the US invasion of Iraq, though it is a bit overt at times about it; the plot structure is laid out well as the movie is pretty linear; flow between sequences is; character writing is good as you do care for these characters and what they want, especially Sophie and Howl"
  }
  screenplay {
    writer {
      name: "Hayao Miyazaki"
    }
    rating: "Pretty Good"
    comments: "The dialogue is pretty good and standard, for English Dub; the humor keeps the movie pretty light-hearted; the symbolism is evident as the movie is a giant allegory for the US invasion of Iraw, even though it can be a bit overt at times; the foreshadowing is decently prevelant"
  }
